text: cea (muhammad) midi mxng du phu thi toyæng xi brxhim nı reuxng phracea khxng khea dxk hrux? Neuxng ca kxallxhˌ di thrng prathan xanac kæ khea khna thi xi brxhim di klaw wa phracea khxng channan khux phu thi thrng hı pen læa thrng hı tay di khea klaw wa kha k hı pen læa hı tay di xi brxhi mk la w wa thæ cring xallxhˌ nan thrng na dwng xathity ma cak this tawanxxk than cng na man ma cak this tawantk theid læw phu thi ptiseth sraththa nan kdi rab khwam ngngngwy læa xallxhˌ nan ca mi thrng prathan næwthang xan thuk txng kæ phu xthrrm thanghlay
